ews/390173|title=龍德造船六廠開工，將打造沱江級後續艦|date=2018-12-30|access-date=2019-01-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190102050522/https://www.peopo.org/news/390173|archive-date=2019-01-02|dead-url=no|publisher=PeoPo公民新聞}}</ref>

